_sText:
Rats Desktop2 is the same map as Rats Desktop BUT it has some additions and changes.
rats_desktop was kept as is because its gameplay is more sniper-oriented.

rats_desktop2 involves more interactivity (try click the mouse) and more adventure (breakable mugs, you can also climb up the computer screen on the post-its).

The map has been revised a bit to prevent its major sniping areas from being abused.
